Name: Dream Jump Adventure
About the game: Classic 8-bit style jumping game where you travel to three lands in your dreams each one harder then the last to complete. Collect golden horse shoes to unlock new noble steeds ranging from a rainbow horse to a lawn mower. Once you have completed each map you will get the chance to uncover the secret message but be warned don't let the look fool you this game can be extremely difficult.
